# Engagement Targets

> Who you comment on, and why. Fill this during/after `/onboard`. Three groups work well —
> adapt to your strategy. Add LinkedIn URLs and the outcome you want from each.

## Group 1 — Bigger voices (borrow their audience)
People with large followings whose audience IS your ICP. You become a familiar, sharp name
in their comments. Their followers find you.
